title: Chinese People HATE Mulan... and it's Hilarious!
description:
Disney tried to prioritize the China market over the rest of the world, and sold its morals with it. Despite the grand effort to appeal to a Chinese audience, Mulan was pirated before release, still flopped, and was decimated from terrible reviews on the Chinese internet. lol.
